snippet.title: Starting an Open Source Project
snippet.description:
Starting An Open Source Project

1 Year Free Hosting:  https://www.atlantic.net/kalle/  Use code KALLE for an additional $50

A lot of people might be wondering how to start an open source project and I am hoping that this video may help a little.

Project: https://github.com/KalleHallden/BookOmatic
